:

1. On se *bori* za svoje pravo. (He is fighting for his right.)
2. Oni *bori* se međusobno. (They are fighting with each other.)
3. Oni se *bori* protiv zla. (They are fighting against evil.)
4. On *bori* se za pravdu. (He is fighting for justice.)
5. Naš narod se *bori* za svoje pravo. (Our nation is fighting for its right.)
6. Oni se *bori* za demokratiju. (They are fighting for democracy.)
7. Oni se *bore* protiv korupcije. (They are fighting against corruption.)
8. Oni se *boru* za slobodu. (They are fighting for freedom.)